'''Pascale Lamche''' (yavutse Nyakanga 1960), ni [[Ubufaransa|Umufaransa]] -Umukinnyi wa firime [[Afurika y’Epfo|muri Afrika yepfo]] . Azwi nk'umuyobozi wa firime nyinshi zizwi cyane harimo ''Stalingrad'', ''Black Diamond'', ''Pakisitani Zindabad'', ''Ubwiza bw'Abafaransa'', ''Ushinjwa # 1: Nelson Mandela'', ''Sophiatown'' na ''Winnie'' .  Usibye gukora firime, ni na producer, umwanditsi akaba n'umukinnyi wa sinema. 

== Umwuga ==
Yabonye icyiciro cya mbere cyicyubahiro BA impamyabumenyi yamateka ya none yakuye muri Kaminuza ya Sussex na Sorbonne . Yatangiye umwuga wa firime i Londere mu kigo cyigenga cya firime, Cinema Action, akora mu kigega cy’iburayi cyandika mu 1989. Icyakora, nyuma yaje kwimukira i Paris gushinga ICONE, umushinga wo gukorana na firime na televiziyo. Yagize amahirwe yo gukorera i Londere na Paris nk'umuproducer n'umuyobozi wigenga. Aherekeza hamwe na societe ''ntoya'' yo gukora documentaire. Nyuma yinjiye muri 'La Cie Phares et Balises' maze aba umuyobozi wa International Co-Productions for Kamera Continentales. 

Muri 2017, yakoze filime documentaire ''Winnie'', ivuga ku buzima bwa Winnie Madikizela-Mandela n'urugamba rwe rwo gusenya Apartheid muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo.   Iyi filime yerekanwe mu rwego rwo kwerekana iserukiramuco ry'uburenganzira bwa muntu 2019.  Muri uwo mwaka, yatsindiye igihembo cy'umuyobozi mwiza wa documentaire mpuzamahanga muri Sundance Festival . 

Muri Mata 2018, Lamche yasobanuye ko uwahoze ari minisitiri w’umutekano n’umutekano           Sydney Mufamadi mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru. 

